(CVE-2018-2622)

* mysql: Server: Optimizer unspecified vulnerability (CPU Jan 2018)
(CVE-2018-2640)

* mysql: Server: Optimizer unspecified vulnerability (CPU Jan 2018)
(CVE-2018-2665)

